title: Gun owners face permit fee hike in Connecticut| Latest News Videos
text:
Gun owners face permit fee hike in Connecticut Feb. 15, 2017 - 1:44 - Gov. Malloy's budget proposal includes increasing the state portion of the pistol permit renewal fee from $70 to $300 and new permits from $140 dollars to $370
